#   _pushpin headline — Axis 13 Config Files).  With tera,
#   Vincent Prouillet becomes a 2-LIBRARY AUTHOR in the
#   taxonomy.  Distinct from David Tolnay (serde / thiserror /
#   anyhow / serde_yaml = 4-library), Sean McArthur
#   (Hyperium / reqwest), Sindre Sorhus (Node CLI utils),
#   François Mockers (notify-rs), Paul Miller (chokidar /
#   noble-crypto), Daniel Abramov (snapview / tungstenite),
#   Vitaly Puzrin (markdown-it / js-yaml = 2-library), Armin
#   Ronacher (console-rs / dialoguer + Python Flask/Jinja2).
#
# (Leaderboard at R673: Rust=76, Go=75, TS-Node=75 — Rust solo
# at the top.  Axis 9 / Logging 6/6/6 three-way symmetric.
# Axes 10 + 13 + 14 at 2/2/2.  Axes 7 + 8 + 11 + 12 + 15 + 16
